-- Markel Acquires IDRECO as Insurer Adds Dredging In Europe
-- B y   S t e v e n   N o r t o n
-- 2012-07-03T21:26:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-03/markel-acquires-idreco-as-insurer-adds-dredging-in-europe.html
Markel Corp. (MKL) , the Virginia-based
insurer, said it acquired IDRECO GmbH to expand its dredging
business to sand and gravel mining in Europe.  IDRECO, based in Heerenberg, the Netherlands, will be part
of Markel’s Ellicott Dredge Enterprises, the insurer said today
in a PR Newswire statement that didn’t disclose terms.  To contact the reporter on this story:
